Description:

Properties for the various charts. The following table summarizes
the relation between each ChartProperty and the chart types.

| ChartProperty     | [barChart] | [pieChart] | [xyChart] |
|:------------------|------------|------------|-----------|
| `areaPlot`        |            |            |    y      |
| `chartSize`       |   y        |     y      |    y      |
| `curvePlot`       |            |            |    y      |
| `horizontal`      |   y        |            |    y      |
| `linePlot`        |            |            |    y      |
| `ring`            |            |     y      |    y      |
| `stackedBars`     |   y        |            |           |
| `subTitle`        |   y        |     y      |    y      |
| `vertical`        |   y        |            |    y      |
| `xLabel`          |   y        |            |    y      |
| `yLabel`          |   y        |            |    y      |


